<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/13 (Thu.) Family Travel/Frozen Fruit and Veggies (Host: Nikki)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=290&amp;p=306#p306"><![CDATA[
Session I: Family Travel<br /><br />Source: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2019/05/27/travel/family-vacation.html">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/201 ... ation.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. What does travel mean to you?<br /><br />2. Have you ever traveled with family? How was the experience?<br /><br />3. Do you like to travel with family? Why or why not?<br /><br />4. Any suggestion for a successful family trip?<br /><br /><br />Session II: Frozen Fruit and Veggies<br /><br />Source: <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cnn.com/2019/05/30/health/frozen-fruit-vegetables-drayer-food/index.html">https://www.cnn.com/2019/05/30/health/f ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2019/05/30/health/frozen-fruit-vegetables-drayer-food/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/05/30/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Do you eat frozen fruit and veggies? Why or why not?<br /><br />2. Do you agree or disagree with the article?Why?<br /><br />3. What are your favorite veggie dishes? <br /><br />4. Do you keep any special diet ? Share with us.<br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. first topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:20 p.m. Presentation <br />8:20 p.m.-- 8:40 p.m. Sharing time : articles &amp; other experiences. <br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第一區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Tue Jun 11, 2019 9:27 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
